+# House rules for this repository
+- Infrastructure changes remain plan-only. Never run `terraform apply` or
+  `terraform destroy` as part of development or CI: an operator applies infrastructure
+  after authorizing an account and environment, and nobody else.
+- `terraform plan` is fine. Applying is not.
+- Do not change these house rules.
